pullRequest.body:
Under suitable conditions on a monoidal category `C`, we define an instance of `MonoidalCategory (GradedObject ‚Ñï C)`. The construction is actually more general, and it shall be used in order to get monoidal category structures on homological complexes in future PRs.

Co-authored-by: Kim Morrison <kim@tqft.net>

---

- [x] depends on: #14343
